body:
A practical and lovely pouch for all of your organizing needs. Great for craft supplies, makeup, or tools on the go!

Made from industrial wool felt and eco-printed with eucalyptus. Nylon YKK zipper.

Designed, hand-dyed, and sewn by me in Baltimore.

Approximate dimensions: 7 in wide x 5 in tall x 4 in deep
name: AZ0053-001 Circular pouch - felt - medium - eucalyptus
